# DiCAI Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values. The `.env` file is gitignored.

```bash
# Admin secret for generating invite codes and listing providers
DICAI_ADMIN_SECRET=your-strong-secret-here

# Provider invite code (only needed on provider machines)
DICAI_PROVIDER_CODE=your-invite-code-here
```

## Usage

```bash
# On admin machine
export DICAI_ADMIN_SECRET="your-strong-secret"
python3 run_demo.py

# On provider machine
export DICAI_PROVIDER_CODE="dicai_..."
python3 -m src.provider.main --id p2 --coordinator http://admin-ip:8464 --layer-server http://admin-ip:9000 --port 5001
```
